text: Einar Møbius (6 August 1891 - 22 November 1981) was a Danish gymnast. He competed in the men's artistic individual all-around event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1891 births Category:1981 deaths Category:Danish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Denmark Category:Gymnasts at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Aarhus
